'''Phiàng-fa-sṳ''' ([[Mîn-tûng-ngî‎]]: Bàng-uâ-cê)，pûn tshṳ̂n-tso “Fuk-chû-fa lò-mâ-sṳ”, he [[Sṳ̍p-kiú sṳ-ki]] tsó-khì lòi [[Fuk-chû]] ke [[Yîn-Mî]] [[tshòn-kau-sṳ]] sat-kie tshut-lòi ke yit-tsúng lâ-tên-fa vùn-sṳ. Phiàng-fa-sṳ tshiùng tsui-tshû ke fông-on to phêu-tsún-fa kîn-li̍t tsṳ̂n-tô pien-fa, yî Sṳ̍p-kiú sṳ-ki ha-pan ya̍p thin-hìn.
Sṳ̍p-kiú sṳ-ki to [[Ngi-sṳ̍p Sṳ̍p-kiú]] song-pan ya̍p, Phiàng-fa-sṳ put-thon hîn-sṳn tshai Fuk-chû-fa thûng-hàng khî ke [[kau-fi]] nui. [[Sṳn-kîn]], Tsan-mî sṳ-si̍p, yî-khi̍p thai-liong ke tshòn-kau tsok-phín tû-voi sṳ́-yung Phiàng-fa-sṳ.

